<head>1407	H.R. 5753 (Seventy-fifth Congress, Third Session &#8212; F. Roosevelt)</head>

<p>Authorizes advance of the amounts due on delinquent homestead entries on certain Indian reservations.</p>

<p>Vetoed April 8, 1938.  The veto message was laid before the House, referred to the Committee on Indian Affairs, and printed as H.R. Doc. No. 582 (83 <title>Cong. Rec.</title> 5124).</p>

<p>Veto unchallenged.</p>


