<p>Mr. SHAFER of Michigan. Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to extend my own remarks and to include therein a communication received from Robert J. Caldwell, of New York.</p>
<p>The SPEAKER. Without objection, it is so ordered. There was no objection.</p>
